                <div class="do__card card">
                    p.do__subtitle Web Development
                    p.do__p We develop the necessary landing pages and websites and launch them in order to convert incoming traffic into leads and orders.
                </div>
                <div class="do__card card">
                    p.do__subtitle Design Process
                    p.do__p We design advertisements and websites.
